{"tid":1095623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"偷拍吃魚喝茶全過程　3人開門他崩潰「勇者鬥惡龍」","createTime":"2019-04-07T07:01:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T10:55:51.000Z","uid":32511,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1b72ba12def90feb70143320a260d3503cd87870","tid":1095623,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T07:01:33.000Z","msg":"「吃魚喝茶」對一般人來說是一件神秘的事情，日前一名中國大陸網友就偷拍了自己叫的小姐，結果其他人看完全都傻眼，笑說「要我倒貼都不去」。<br />\n<br />\n一名中國大陸網友日前去挑戰「喝茶」，還趁著對方開門時迅速將長相拍下，第1人開門時該網友想著再找找更好的，想不到隨著第2人、第3人開門後，網友的「慾火」已經完全熄滅，最後只能在網路上PO文，大嘆「現在的工作室質量不談了」。<br />\n<br />\n其他人看到後也說「快逃啊」、「我X，怎麼全是掃地阿姨」、「這一張張照片都看的我心慌」、「越往下滑越害怕，這是怎麼一回事」、「我只想問樓主最後有沒付錢」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/05/12/1356543-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F1356543-XXL.jpg&h=e50683ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/05/12/1356542-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F1356542-XXL.jpg&h=7ea3cfc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/05/12/1356544-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F1356544-XXL.jpg&h=919e6a21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2c4ab010d9db313415f3a4bb072e05406a4ac1c","tid":1095623,"uid":81113,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T07:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/odhUjht.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FodhUjht.png&h=12f3742e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dcea4a60a8136c9d4c28219b103ff0d941644608","tid":1095623,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T07:04:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"752ef6dfb7c96188ebf8ca9fd7311a7a8f38315a","tid":1095623,"uid":153827,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":2